i><b>Obserwuj stany magazynowe<\/b> &#8211; Regularnie sprawdzaj poziom zapas\u00f3w i dostosowuj wydatki na reklam\u0119, aby unikn\u0105\u0107 wyczerpania towar\u00f3w.<\/li>\n<li><b>Skorzystaj z danych<\/b> &#8211; Monitoruj wyniki kampanii i b\u0105d\u017a gotowy na zmiany strategii w oparciu o trendy sprzeda\u017cowe.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, kluczowe jest aktywne zaanga\u017cowanie w kampanie oraz strategiczne podej\u015bcie do ich optymalizacji. Przygotuj si\u0119 na sezon zakupowy z wyprzedzeniem, a Twoje wyniki mog\u0105 by\u0107 znakomite!<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak skutecznie przygotowa\u0107 kampanie PPC na Black Friday i Cyber Monday?<\/h2>\n<p>Ju\u017c nied\u0142ugo na<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":7032,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7031","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-strategia"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7031"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7031"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7031\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7032"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7031"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/catego